Basic bank account
A bank account only for people who don't hold another UK current account or don't qualify for our other current accounts.

More about FlexBasic
Overdrafts
An arranged overdraft is designed for short-term borrowing. We’ll look at your circumstances to see if we can offer you one.

Overdrafts
Switching to Nationwide
There are lots of ways you can switch your bank account to us. Most people do a full switch using the Current Account Switch Service. It's a free service and will complete in just 7 working days.

More about switching bank account

Get 5% cashback on your supermarket shop
With everything going up, get a little back. For a limited time, our adult and student current account members can now earn up to £10 cashback a month at a wide range of supermarkets and convenience stores. Terms and conditions apply.

More about our cashback
